48,"uid":25055,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T12:27:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>華人去外國，最叻咪係開食肆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根本就溶入唔到人地社會</blockquote><br />\n掛中國菜都好多鬼佬buy 通常都好難食 <br />\n搵錢快做十年已經有樓有車 好運既未夠廿年賣生意退休 入咩主流社會自己生活舒適就得 <br />\n<br />\n下一代已經係亞裔local</blockquote><br />\n基本細個唔係當地讀書好難有鬼佬圈子 <br />\n<br />\n要有鬼佬圈子真係細細個讀local school"},{"pid":"de625afa4bb29875d639e4cef0ed670a942ae182","tid":442548,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T14:14:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>90年代便隨家人移民澳洲。他憶述當年移民澳洲，因為家境不好，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當年有手有腳就過到去 , 依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f27b434138b92be748cb558be8d804f2c1e0106","tid":442548,"uid":43117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T14:31:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>90年代便隨家人移民澳洲。他憶述當年移民澳洲，因為家境不好，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正常係調返轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21c6a9d5024636c9fe98fa8171252a0887edfe1","tid":442548,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T15:21:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">維撚黨報毒果點解唔查下，支那種咁撚多年有幾多咁既移民&quot;勵志&quot;上位，其中又有幾多唔係做鬼佬唔會做既偷雞厄先上到位？？？</span></span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}